# Why Python?
----------------
• Python is a versatile and powerful programming language.
›It's ability to handle complex calculations, analyze large dataset, and automate processes has made it an invaluable tool for engineers.
--------------------------------------
# Advantages
-----------------
• Extensive Libraries
• Free and Open Source
• Extensible
• Simple and Easy
• Embeddable
--------------------------------------
# Disadvantages of Python
------------------
Speed Limitations
Weak in Mobile Computing and Browsers
Design Restrictions
Underdeveloped Database Access Layers
---------------------------------------
# Python for Software
-------------------
• Data Analysis and Machine Learning
• Web Development
• Automation or scripting
• Software Testing and Prototyping
• Everyday Tasks
